   in this repository.

   "SIUKS Course" refers to the university course "Създаване на Интерактивно 
   Учебно Компютърно Съдържание" (Creating Interactive Educational Computer 
   Content) taught at the Faculty of Mathematics and Informatics, Sofia 
   University "St. Kliment Ohridski".

   "Educational Submission" means any work submitted for academic credit,
   grading, or evaluation in the SIUKS Course or any substantially similar
   course at any educational institution.

